  <div class="block-3">
    <div class="inner-block">
      <section class="biography" id="biography">
        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Sally sits on the Departmental Board and is also a member of the Audit and Risk Assurance Committee. Sally’s executive career was at Lloyds Banking Group where she held a wide range of general management roles. Sally now serves as a Non-Executive Director (NED) on a number of Boards including the Principality Building Society, Hafren Dyfrdwy Ltd, part of Severn Trent Group Plc, and as a Trustee Director at Tearfund, the Christian relief and development charity.</p>

</div>
      </section>

      <div class="current-roles" id="current-roles">
          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_3968">
            <h1 id="non-executive-director">Non-executive Director</h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>Non-executive directors provide an external perspective on DFID’s work, while knowing and understanding DFID as an organisation.</p>

<p>They use their experiences and skills from outside DFID to provide objective and constructive challenges on the decisions made by DFID’s committees and boards.</p>

<p>The Non-executive Director sits on the following committees and boards within DFID:</p>

<ul>
  <li>the Departmental Board</li>
  <li>the Executive Management Committee</li>
  <li>the Audit Committee</li>
</ul>

<p>Non-executive directors form a network across government, led by the Government Lead Non-executive.</p>
</div>
            <div class="read-more">
